snappystream
------------------------------------------
There is snappy compressor from google, but it doesn't have default stream
realisation. This project aim to release C++ stream for snappy with format,
compatible with java realisation by Dain Sundstrom. So you can use, for
example, java realisation for compression and C++ for decompression, or vice
versa.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libsnappy1-1.2.2-1
  libsnappystream-devel-1.0.0-1bl2
  libsnappystream1-1.0.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  libsnappy-devel-1.2.2-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/hoxnox/snappystream

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/hoxnox/snappystream/archive/refs/tags/1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack snappystream-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./snappystream-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/snappystream-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/snappystream-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsnappystream1-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsnappystream-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(snappystream)
  /usr/bin/snappystream-crc32c.exe
  /usr/bin/snappystream-snap.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/snappystream.README
  /usr/share/doc/snappystream/README.md

(libsnappystream1)
  /usr/bin/cygsnappystream-1.dll

(libsnappystream-devel)
  /usr/include/snappystream/InputSnappyStreamBoostFilter.hpp
  /usr/include/snappystream/OutputSnappyStreamBoostFilter.hpp
  /usr/include/snappystream/isnappystream.hpp
  /usr/include/snappystream/osnappystream.hpp
  /usr/include/snappystream/snappystream.hpp
  /usr/include/snappystream/snappystreamcfg.hpp
  /usr/lib/libsnappystream.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/snappystream.pc

